room_title: Escape room "Mysterious Temple" by Out Of Time Escape in Charlotte
room_address: 16325 Northcross Drive, Suite B, Huntersville, NC 28078
room_description: Your group is on a camping trip in the Pisgah National forest. Your stumble across a mysterious hidden Temple and decide to set up base camp next to it to investigate. Is there a way in? Can you follow the clues to find the hidden treasure or will it turn into your final resting place?
